===============
= Boom Engine =
===============

About
-----
Boom is a game engine for 3d bomberman-like games.

Build requirements
------------------
freeglut3-dev
libsdl1.2-dev
libsdl1.2-mixer-dev
libpng12-dev
libsigc++-2.0-dev
scons

Building
--------
Just type 'scons' into a terminal. Use 'scons -c' to clean.

Running
-------
There is no installation procedure yet, so to run the demo please use the included run.sh and rundemo.sh scripts. e.g. './rundemo.sh' to run the demo, './run.sh tools/bmeshview player walking' to run the mesh viewer so that the library is loaded properly.
